data.description: Move Right In! This 3-bed, 1.5-bath home is ready for you to begin enjoying! Conveniently located near downtown Sturgis, this spacious home is sure to match what you have been looking for. When you walk in, you will notice the open-concept kitchen that leads directly to the living area. Here, you are sure to fall in love with the original wood floors and amazing woodwork. You are also sure to be pleased by the 3 large bedrooms along with the newly remodeled bathroom in 2024! The basement offers a bonus area to enjoy family time, or a possible exercise room. Don't forget the 2-car detached garage! Call today for a personal showing!
